50|$|Peus, son of Friedrich-Carl Peus {{and first}} cousin of German numismatist Busso Peus (24 October 1902 - 18 November 1983), studied {{law at the}} {{universities}} of Heidelberg, Vienna and Münster and received a doctoral degree (Dr. jur.) from the University of Heidelberg. In 1933, he joined his father's law office in Münster as a <b>solicitor</b> <b>and</b> <b>barrister</b> <b>and</b> as a notary.|$|R
