25|$|The legal bodies {{governing}} {{the conduct of}} <b>solicitors</b> <b>and</b> <b>barristers</b> are the Law Society of Hong Kong and the Hong Kong Bar Association, respectively. There are currently three law schools offering the Postgraduate Certificate in Laws, required for starting work as a trainee solicitor or pupil barrister.|$|R
